# ğŸ§  AI PDF Summariser

A full-stack web application that allows users to upload PDF documents and generate either **short**
or **detailed summaries** using Google's **Gemini API**. Built with **React**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Flask**,
the app provides a fast and intuitive experience for summarizing long documents.
Summaries can be copied directly or downloaded as PDF files.

